2219408ec0a5a5470dc697a77d1aa5dfa9cbeb35.query:
SELECT path as file_path 
    FROM files JOIN share_link_files ON share_link_files.file_id=files.id 
    WHERE files.id=$1 AND share_link_files.share_link_id=$2

501d8d7f066fc8fd5f790228f23f533decbadd93.query: INSERT INTO share_links (id, expiration, created_at) VALUES ($1, $2, $3)

812aa12b1dcfb7fffcdf87db7b813850f8933c38.query:
SELECT files.path AS filename, files.id AS link, '' AS short_filename
    FROM share_links JOIN share_link_files ON share_links.id=share_link_files.share_link_id 
    JOIN files ON share_link_files.file_id=files.id 
    WHERE share_links.id=$1
